                    <usg type="warring-states-currency">3</usg>
                </gramGrp>
  <def>read texts (more or less) aloud for oneself</def>
            </sense>
<sense xml:id="uuid-56f3b848-ae89-424c-9328-b696b109fae1" n="27">
<gramGrp>
                    <pos>V</pos>
  <tls:syn-func corresp="#uuid-fbfb2371-2537-4a99-a876-41b15ec2463c">vtoN</tls:syn-func>
                    <usg type="warring-states-currency">5</usg>
                </gramGrp>
  <def>read out, recite or at least mumble (usually prose); pronounce cf. even Jin Yong: 讀給他聽。　聽清客讀了，很感興味。</def>
